{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "f6598a7c-2287-4ee6-ab14-d83916ee0d1c",
    "name": "MEZ05: Sea Caves Danger",
    "sceneId": "f1d169df-e10e-451d-8481-0d0290b7cbbe",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "e7737c99-9ee5-46f3-b33b-68454a4901e0",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                    "id": "79ef70e6-ec9c-47fa-bb2c-d4feabeb0927",
                    "scope": "scene",
                    "scopeId": "f1d169df-e10e-451d-8481-0d0290b7cbbe",
                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                    "tagsToAdd": "hadSeaCaveDanger",
                    "tagsToRemove": null
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1d54f892-783b-4fac-863e-97aa7e70b8bf",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are you sure we are doing the right thing leaving the secret passageway to the Sea Caves open? You know how dangerous that area can be.",
                    "emotion": "2",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "1",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b1a4674d-afbf-4376-af1c-3012cdf7ddcc",
                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "These aren't children we are dealing with here at the University, Silvia. They need the opportunity to prove to themselves that they have the skills to survive.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "1",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "dd0da194-80c1-4a8b-a645-197a8aa35d28",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Don't worry, Silvia, the passageway is well-concealed. It takes skill and persistence to find it. So I'm not too concerned about the sea caves. Most students will never find the hidden door.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "1",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "63bb5151-082e-4e15-9371-0acece202f13",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "And as for the ones who do find it? We are all doing our best to train these students to use their wisdom and their skills to survive. They are going to face danger in the outside world. At least in the sea caves, they are staying relatively close to the school and to safety.\n",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "1",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c42ba0d7-f88f-4653-9510-4c91d9bd3380",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I do hope you are both correct. I would hate for anything to happen like it did at the 'How to Be a Hero' school.",
                    "emotion": "2",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "1",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "196b21e3-a229-4cee-b1c8-6de02909f35f",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We'll all work to make sure that sort of thing never happens here in Sardonia, Silvia. I promise you that.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "1",
                    "device2": "0"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}